{"tid":300689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1晚放近4萬枚煙花　23分鐘燒1,200萬","createTime":"2017-06-28T06:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T06:25:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3d26cfea61f3c26715a398fd984fa0bf37e70d","tid":300689,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:17:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498629427_f380.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170628%2Flarge%2F1498629427_f380.jpg&d=anOzd1FYTW2EZ%2B0L9%2Fb%2F9O9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=ee444cee\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170628/large/1498629427_f380.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n為慶祝香港主權移交中國廿周年，港府不惜再度大灑金錢於7.1當晚放煙花。康文署稱當晚8點將在維港上空上演歷時23分鐘的煙花匯演，由5艘躉船發放合共39,888枚煙花彈，並會用在灣仔金紫荊廣場沿岸的光束燈及香港會議展覽中心玻璃幕牆上的LED屏幕﹐以多媒體技術為煙花匯演增添視覺效果，市民可在匯演中看到「紅色的心型笑臉」等圖案。<br />\n<br />\n康文署表示，煙花匯演共分8幕，除了「紅色的心型笑臉」，更會有小蝴蝶、波板糖和氣球等圖案，最後一幕則有長達23秒的密集式煙。根據當局早前公佈，今次匯演首次用上一枚禮花彈先後完成「笑臉」及「紅心」的圖案變換，第一幕「香港&bull;我家」更會出現20次用紅色簡體字寫出「中国HK」的字樣。<br />\n<br />\n今次匯演由香港廣東社團總會、香港中國商會、中滔環保集團和飛達帽業控股4間公司贊助，當局曾稱預算總贊助金額達1,200萬港元。"},{"pid":"0cabdd8e54dfc707fe5274fe926df2e1673c9965","tid":300689,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c49809b0c663aa2e3ff933ef00248c6fd7901e58","tid":300689,"uid":42586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"不要說 煙花    試着說 空氣污染"},{"pid":"d5505c6ec35238eb0aecccbf2aa5a190d1c5d2d0","tid":300689,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27ae8737af9cb03450ce61c6ba693f8d796af3d","tid":300689,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"買到幾多罐午餐肉呀 23分鐘呀屌"},{"pid":"aee9167e3255e9a2bedb131e1d4133a541a9c39b","tid":300689,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"未見過煙花係咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以叫煙火係有道理，係一堆亂鳩咁燒嘅海上火警嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/ftp/News/20170613/HK/_13GK002_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20170613%2FHK%2F_13GK002_.jpg&h=38a19c0a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}